2canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fraveena-tandon-steers-clear-on-her-suicide-rumours-which-came-after-she-broke-up-with-akshay-kumar-i-was-fine-the-bigger-fuss-was-made-in-the-media%2Farticleshow%2F108845045.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Anurag%20Thakur%20Blasts%20UN%20Body%20Report%20On%20Unemployment%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20today%20disputed%20the%20data%20put%20out%20by%20the%20International%20Labour%20Organisation%20which%20said%20that%20employment%20scenario%20in%20India%20is%20grim%2C%20especially%20among%20youth.%20ILO%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20stated%20that%20youth%20form%20nearly%2083%25%20of%20the%20unemployed%20workforce%20in%20India.%20The%20study%20also%20showed%20that%20the%20number%20of%20educated%20youth%20among%20all%20jobless%20people%20has%20gone%20up%20from%2054.2%25%20to%2065.7%25%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20indicates%20that%20the%20problem%20of%20unemployment%20in%20India%20has%20become%20increasingly%20concentrated%20among%20the%20youth%2C%20especially%20the%20educated%20ones%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Youth%20Affairs%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20said%20that%20the%20data%20by%20Indian%20agencies%20painted%20a%20different%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B64%20million%20people%20have%20registered%20on%20Employees'%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20(EPFO).%20It%20is%20a%20bigger%20number%20than%20the%20population%20of%20Australia%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20many%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakur%20said%20at%20the%20NDTV%20Yuva%20Conclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%2034%20crore%20mudra%20loans%20that%20were%20given%20out%2C%20these%20are%20also%20creating%20job%20opportunities.%20Now%20they%20are%20job%20givers%20from%20being%20job%20seekers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20ILO%20report%2C%20he%20said%20that%20India%20has%20been%20relying%20on%20international%20rating%20agencies%20for%20years%2C%20but%20it%20should%20now%20go%20by%20the%20data%20from%20domestic%20ones%20which%20are%20now%20equally%20equipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20still%20have%20a%20slave%20mentality%20because%20we%20always%20depended%20on%20foreign%20ratings.%20We%20need%20to%20come%20out%20of%20it%20and%20trust%20organisations%20in%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakur%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20for%20youth%20affairs%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20since%20taking%20office%20in%202014%2C%20has%20also%20made%20policies%20to%20aid%20entrepreneurs%2C%20which%20is%20another%20way%20the%20government%20is%20generating%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20people%20do%20not%20hesitate%20while%20launching%20a%20start-up.%20I%20have%20met%20so%20many%20people%20who%20studied%20at%20prestigious%20universities%20and%20took%20up%20jobs%20outside%20India%2C%20have%20now%20come%20back%20and%20are%20now%20running%20a%20start-up%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ILO%20report%20claimed%20that%20India%20would%20add%2070-80%20lakh%20youths%20to%20the%20labour%20workforce%20in%20the%20next%20decade%20if%20it%20worked%20on%205%20policy%20areas%3A%20job%20creation%3B%20quality%20of%20employment%3B%20inequalities%20in%20the%20labour%20market%3B%20strengthening%20both%20skills%20and%20policies%20of%20the%20active%20labour%20market%3B%20and%20bridging%20the%20knowledge%20deficits%20on%20labour%20market%20patterns%20and%20youth%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711614420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-03%2Fjqf05t9g_unemployment_625x300_02_March_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-anurag-thakur-blasts-un-body-report-on-un