Claim%20Group%20Trying%20To%20%26quot%3BDefame%20Courts%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20lawyers%2C%20including%20senior%20advocate%20Harish%20Salve%20and%20Bar%20Council%20of%20India%20chairperson%20Manan%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20have%20written%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20alleging%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bvested%20interest%20group%26quot%3B%20is%20trying%20to%20pressure%20the%20judiciary%20and%20defame%20courts%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20basis%20of%20frivolous%20logic%20and%20stale%20political%20agendas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20pressure%20tactics%20are%20most%20obvious%20in%20political%20cases%2C%20particularly%20those%20involving%20political%20figures%20accused%20of%20corruption.%20These%20tactics%20are%20damaging%20to%20our%20courts%20and%20threaten%20our%20democratic%20fabric%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20letter%2C%20dated%20March%2026%2C%20addressed%20to%20CJI%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20shared%20by%20official%20sources%2C%20targeted%20a%20section%20of%20lawyers%20without%20naming%20them%20and%20alleged%20that%20they%20defend%20politicians%20by%20the%20day%20and%20then%20try%20to%20influence%20judges%20through%20the%20media%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20interest%20group%20creates%20false%20narratives%20of%20a%20supposed%20better%20past%20and%20golden%20period%20of%20courts%2C%20contrasting%20it%20with%20the%20happenings%20in%20the%20present%2C%20the%20letter%20said%2C%20claiming%20that%20their%20comments%20are%20aimed%20at%20influencing%20courts%20and%20embarrassing%20them%20for%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20of%20lawyers%2C%20who%20are%20behind%20the%20letter%20titled%20%26quot%3BJudiciary%20Under%20Threat-Safeguarding%20Judiciary%20from%20Political%20and%20Professional%20Pressure%26quot%3B%2C%20number%20around%20600%20and%20also%20include%20Adish%20Aggarwala%2C%20Chetan%20Mittal%2C%20Pinky%20Anand%2C%20Hitesh%20Jain%2C%20Ujjwala%20Pawar%2C%20Uday%20Holla%20and%20Swarupama%20Chaturvedi%2C%20the%20official%20sources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20lawyers%20behind%20the%20letter%20have%20mentioned%20no%20specific%20cases%2C%20the%20development%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20courts%20are%20dealing%20with%20several%20high-profile%20criminal%20cases%20of%20corruption%20involving%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20accused%20the%20central%20government%20of%20targeting%20their%20leaders%20as%20part%20of%20its%20political%20vendetta%2C%20a%20charge%20refuted%20by%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%20These%20parties%2C%20whose%20ranks%20include%20some%20noted%20lawyers%2C%20have%20joined%20hands%20against%20the%20recent%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy-linked%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20critics%2C%20these%20lawyers%20have%20accused%20them%20of%20suggesting%20that%20courts%20in%20the%20past%20were%20easier%20to%20influence.%20This%20shakes%20the%20public's%20trust%20in%20courts%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20antics%20are%20vitiating%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20trust%20and%20harmony%2C%20which%20characterises%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20judiciary%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20their%20letter%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20concocted%20an%20entire%20theory%20of%20%26quot%3Bbench%20fixing%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20not%20just%20disrespectful%20and%20contemptuous%20but%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20honour%20and%20dignity%20of%20courts%2C%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20also%20stooped%20to%20the%20level%20of%20comparing%20our%20courts%20to%20those%20countries%20where%20there%20is%20no%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20accusing%20our%20judicial%20institutions%20with%20unfair%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20critics%20have%20adopted%20the%20%26quot%3Bmy%20way%20or%20the%20highway%26quot%3B%20approach%20at%20work%20as%20they%20hail%20the%20decisions%20they%20agree%20with%2C%20but%20any%20decision%20they%20disagree%20with%2C%20is%20trashed%2C%20smeared%20and%20disregarded%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20two-faced%20behaviour%20is%20harmful%20to%20the%20respect%20a%20common%20man%20should%20have%20for%20our%20legal%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said%20and%20claimed%20that%20this%20cherry%20picking%20has%20been%20visible%20in%20very%20recent%20judgments%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20elements%20are%20trying%20to%20influence%20who%20the%20judges%20are%20in%20their%20cases%20and%20spread%20lies%20on%20social%20media%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20them%20to%20decide%20in%20a%20particular%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20alleged%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20the%20timing%2C%20the%20lawyers%20said%20it%20is%20all%20happening%20when%20the%20country%20is%20headed%20for%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20reminded%20of%20similar%20antics%20in%202018-2019%20when%20they%20took%20to%20their%20'hit%20and%20run'%20activities%2C%20including%20fabricating%20wrong%20narratives.%20These%20efforts%20to%20belittle%20and%20manipulate%20the%20courts%20for%20personal%20and%20political%20reasons%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20under%20any%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20urged%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20stand%20strong%20and%20take%20steps%20to%20protect%20courts%20from%20these%20alleged%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStaying%20silent%20or%20doing%20nothing%20could%20accidentally%20give%20more%20power%20to%20those%20who%20mean%20to%20do%20harm.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20maintain%20dignified%20silence%20as%20such%20efforts%20are%20happening%20since%20few%20years%20and%20too%20frequently%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20CJI's%20