esses%20to%20come%20forward%20after%20the%20victim%20was%20reported%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Bserious%20injuries%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Do%20Social%20Media%20Campaigns%20Affect%20Voting%20Patterns%20In%20India%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7qf3lsn_online-effect_625x300_28_March_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20five%20years%20have%20passed%20since%20I%20started%20my%20study.%20Now%2C%20elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner%20again%20for%20most%20of%20the%20states%20that%20I%20analysed.%20Will%20I%20put%20the%20Singh-Srivastava%20Vote%20Predictor%2C%20a%20statistical%20model%20that%20correlates%20political%20communication%20on%20Twitter%20with%20actual%20vote%20share%2C%20through%20its%20paces%20once%20more%3F%20It%20would%20certainly%20be%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%20There%20is%20nothing%20more%20robust%20than%20testing%20and%20retesting%20a%20model%20at%20regular%20intervals%20to%20measure%20its%20efficacy.%20But%20this%20is%20a%20humongous%20exercise%2C%20so%20I%20will%20not%20be%20doing%20it%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20policy%20of%20the%20platform%20has%20also%20changed%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftwitter-to-restrict-number-of-posts-users-can-read-says-elon-musk-4170147%5C%22%3Ewith%20Musk%20relying%20more%20on%20automation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20less%20on%20human%20interface%20to%20manage%20Twitter.%20Several%20alterations%20have%20also%20been%20made%20to%20the%20platform's%20APIs.%20This%20affects%20the%20significant%20community%20of%20developers%20who%20now%20must%20rewire%20and%20tweak%20their%20processes%20of%20data%20acquisition%20and%20curation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20study%20was%20completed%20long%20before%20these%20changes%20on%20the%20Twitter%20platform%20were%20even%20a%20gleam%20in%20Elon%20Musk's%20eye.%20Nevertheless%2C%20even%20after%20these%20changes%2C%20the%20Singh-Srivastava%20Vote%20Predictor%20stands%20firm%20because%20it%20simply%20measures%20the%20engagement%20that%20politicians%20and%20political%20parties%20receive%20on%20Twitter%20and%20correlates%20this%20online%20engagement%20with%20a%20predictive%20vote%20share%20offline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implications%20of%20this%20are%20huge%20because%20it%20shows%20that%20the%20impact%20of%20an%20online%20campaign%20can%20genuinely%20be%20measured%20in%20real%20life.%20However%2C%20this%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20online%20campaigns%20can%20be%20a%20substitute%20for%20offline%20campaigns.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20the%20months%20preceding%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-results-2019-election-results-today-counting-of-votes-begins-at-8-am-10-points-2041540%5C%22%3E2019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Frahul-gandhi-speech%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20received%20better%20average%20engagement%20on%20Twitter%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpm-modi%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20that%20didn't%20translate%20into%20a%20win%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20because%20their%20offline%20campaign%20strategy%20was%20weak%20compared%20to%20that%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Online%20campaigns%20can%20add%20value%20to%20the%20brand%20of%20a%20political%20actor%2C%20but%20they%20need%20to%20be%20complemented%20with%20similar%20offline%20strategies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20mass%20mobilisation%20of%20the%20party%20cadre%20and%20supporters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20finding%20also%20shows%20that%20political%20actors%20cannot%20use%20Twitter%20randomly%2C%20or%20only%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20elections.%20If%20they%20don't%20engage%20with%20their%20audience%2024%2F7%2C%20they%20lose%20their%20traction.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20what%20matters%20is%20engagement%2C%20not%20the%20number%20of%20tweets.%20As%20I%20showed%20in%20Chapter%203%2C%20more%20tweets%20do%20not%20necessarily%20mean%20more%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20significant%20implication%20of%20my%20study%20is%20that%20the%20digital%20divide%20between%20richer%20and%20poorer%20states%20in%20India%20is%20closing.%20The%20seven%20states%20I%20analysed%20ranged%20from%20the%20more%20developed%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%20to%20the%20poorer%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Jharkhand%3B%20yet%20by%20measuring%20the%20engagement%20of%20the%20state%20politicians%20and%20political%20parties%20in%20their%20Twitter%20campaigns%2C%20I%20was%20successfully%20able%20to%20predict%20party%20vote%20share%20even%20in%20less%20developed%20states.%20The%20primary%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20the%20digital%20revolution%20of%202016%20that%20resulted%20in%20a%20truly%20digital%20consumption%20society.%20The%20number%20of%20internet%20users%20in%20India%20went%20up%20exponentially%20between%202014%20(approximately%2025%20crore)%20to%202019%20(64%20crore)%2C%20which%20was%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%2091.1%20crore%20people%20eligible%20to%20vote%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20why%20the%20findings%20of%20my%20study%20so%20accurately%20reflected%20the%20results%20achieved%20by%20traditional%20offline%20campaigns.%20It%20is%20clear%20now%20that%20political%20actors%20cannot%20afford%20to%20ignore%20Twitter%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20their%20activities.%20The%20blurring%20of%20the%20online%20and%20offline%20worlds%20will%20probably%20continue%20to%20increase%2C%20making%20social%20media%20a%20true%20part%20of%20the%20real%20world%20and%20changing%20the%20nature%20of%20politics%20even%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20there%20is%20no%20escaping%20social%20media%20for%20political%20leaders.%20The%20more%20people%20identify%20with%20them%20online%2C%20the%20higher%20their%20chances%20of%20engagement%20and%20the%20potential%20conversion%20of%20this%20engagement%20into%20vote%20shares%20during%20elections.%20Engagement%20means%20involvement%20in%20constant%20two-way%20communication%20with%20users%2C%20exchanging%20ideas%20and%20information%2C%20and%20thus%20helping%20grow%20a%20support%20base%20far%20and%20wide.%20Consistency%20of%20thought%20is%20also%20key%20to%20ensuring%20that%20political%20leaders%20can%20command%20a%20loyal%20online%20support%20base.%20Political%20leaders%20need%20to%20be%20consistent%20with%20their%20views%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20are%20not%20limiting%20their%20followers%20to%20just%20their%20or%20their%20party%20views%20but%20exposing%20them%20to%20a%20global%20space%20where%20they%20can%20gain%20knowledge%20and%20expand%20their%20social%20network%20to%20include%20others%20who%20follow%20the%20same%20leaders%20or%20leaders%20with%20similar%20functioning%20traits%20across%20the%20world.%20Consistent%20effort%20on%20the%20part%20of%20political%20leaders%20to%20constantly%20lend%20an%20ear%20to%20their%20support%20base%20and%20keep%20them%20informed%20of%20the%20latest%20practices%2Finformation%2C%20etc.%20can%20be%20used%20to%20their%20political%20advantage%20at%20the%20right%20time%20during%20elections.%20They%20also%20need%20to%20engage%20with%20followers%20who%20react%20negatively%20to%20their%20posts.%20This%20is%20important%20because%20it%20shows%20that%20they%20are%20open%20to%20criticism%20and%20willing%20to%20discuss%20issues%2C%20and%20it%20also%20puts%20them%20in%20a%20position%20to%20convince%20angry%20followers%20of%20their%20intentions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3