Fv%3DYwWVqTy4Ofg%26ab_channel%3DNTSBgov%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficials%20boarded%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-we-know-dali-francis-scott-crash-collapse-maryland-bridge-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESingapore-flagged%20Dali%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20inspection%20on%20Tuesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20NTSB%20hazmat%20investigator%20identified%20the%2056%20hazardous%20containers%20while%20observing%20the%20cargo%20and%20manifest%2C%20Homendy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20764%20tons%20of%20hazardous%20materials.%20Mostly%20corrosives%2C%20flammables%2C%20and%20some%20miscellaneous%20hazardous%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20board%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20containers%20held%20%26quot%3Bclass%209%26quot%3B%20materials%2C%20which%20may%20include%20lithium-ion%20batteries%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHomendy%20added%20that%20she%20saw%20that%20some%20hazardous%20material%20containers%20were%20%26quot%3Bbreached%20significantly%26quot%3B%20and%20several%20had%20fallen%20into%20the%20Patapsco%20River%2C%20but%20did%20not%20have%20%26quot%3Ban%20exact%20number.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20have%20also%20%26quot%3Bseen%20sheen%20on%20the%20waterway%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENTSB%20officials%20said%20the%20exact%20kinds%20of%20hazardous%20materials%20on%20the%20Dali%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20and%20could%20not%20speak%20to%20the%20risks%20posed%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20people%20should%20be%20concerned%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bsheen%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20river%2C%20Homendy%20said%20the%20transportation%20safety%20agency%20had%20referred%20the%20information%20to%20other%20federal%20and%20state%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%20and%20the%20Maryland%20Department%20of%20the%20Environment%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20also%20contacted%20two%20organizations%20researching%20water%20quality%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20Chesapeake%20Research%20Consortium%20and%20Blue%20Water%20Baltimore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20massive%20undertaking%20for%20an%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Homendy%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20total%20probe%20into%20the%20ship's%20malfunctions%20could%20take%2012%20to%2024%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dali%20lost%20power%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20and%20crashed%20into%20Baltimore's%20Key%20Bridge%2C%20causing%20its%20span%20to%20collapse.%20Six%20construction%20workers%20who%20were%20on%20the%20bridge%20have%20died%20or%20are%20presumed%20dead%2C%20with%20four%20bodies%20still%20unrecovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vessel%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-increasing-size-of-container-ships-collapsed-baltimore-bridge-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egross%20tonnage%20of%2095%2C000%20tons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20the%20containers%20carrying%20hazardous%20materials%20would%20have%20taken%20up%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20its%20total%20carrying%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Key%20Bridge's%20collapse%20has%20not%20been%20declared%20a%20chemical-related%20emergency%20as%20of%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20hazardous%20materials%20will%20likely%20complicate%20the%20city's%20clean-up%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pretty%20dangerous%20situation%20in%20that%20area%2C%20and%20we%20can't%20go%20in%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Homendy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20major%20disaster%2C%20when%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fohio-train-derailment-could-cause-explosion-east-palestine-authorities-warn-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrain%20carrying%20toxic%20chemicals%20derailed%20in%20East%20Palestine%2C%20Ohi%2Co%3C%2Fa%3E%20