tle%22%3A%22Will%20bridge%20collapse%20hurt%20global%20supply%20chains%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711606424000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108840351%2Cimgsize-1223259.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwill-bridge-collapse-hurt-global-supply-chains%2Farticleshow%2F108839520.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108839520.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwill-bridge-collapse-hurt-global-supply-chains%2Farticleshow%2F108839520.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwill-bridge-collapse-hurt-global-supply-chains%2Famp_articleshow%2F108839520.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwill-bridge-collapse-hurt-global-supply-chains%2Famp_articleshow%2F108839520.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Human%20Brains%20Getting%20Bigger%2C%20And%20It's%20Good%20News%20For%20Some%3A%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20size%20of%20human%20brain%20is%20increasing%2C%20a%20new%20study%20has%20revealed.%20It%20added%20that%20this%20gradual%20increase%20could%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20dementia%20in%20younger%20generations.%20The%20research%2C%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamaneurology%2Ffullarticle%2F2816798%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJAMA%20Neurology%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20based%20on%20the%20image%20analysis%20of%20more%20than%203%2C000%20participants%20in%20the%20US%20who%20were%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2055%20and%2065.%20The%20team%20from%20University%20of%20California%20(UC)%20Davis%20Health%20concluded%20that%20those%20born%20in%20the%201970s%20(Generation%20X)%20have%20a%206.6%20per%20cent%20greater%20overall%20brain%20volume%20than%20those%20born%20in%20the%201930s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20that%20Generation%20X%20has%208%20per%20cent%20greater%20volume%20of%20white%20matter%20and%2015%20per%20cent%20more%20gray%20matter%20than%20the%20member%20of%20the%20previous%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hippocampus%2C%20which%20plays%20a%20major%20role%20in%20memory%20in%20learning%2C%20expanded%20by%205.7%20per%20cent%20in%20volume%20compared%20to%20previous%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20was%20perceptible%20even%20after%20considering%20other%20factors%20like%20height%2C%20age%20and%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20was%20led%20by%20Charles%20DeCarli%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%20Davis%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20decade%20someone%20is%20born%20appears%20to%20impact%20brain%20size%20and%20potentially%20long-term%20brain%20health.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenetics%20plays%20a%20major%20role%20in%20determining%20brain%20size%2C%20but%20our%20findings%20indicate%20external%20influences%20-%20such%20as%20health%2C%20social%2C%20cultural%20and%20educational%20factors%20-%20may%20also%20play%20a%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencealert.com%2Fyounger-generations-have-larger-brains-is-that-healthier%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScience%20Alert%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researcher%20said%20the%20increased%20size%20of%20the%20brain%20will%20lead%20to%20increased%20reserve%20against%20the%20diseases%20of%20aging%2C%20%26quot%3Bconsequently%20reducing%20overall%20risk%20of%20dementia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disease%20affects%20millions%20of%20people%20across%20the%20world%2C%20especially%20due%20to%20increase%20in%20ageing%20population%20in%20many%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20study%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20line%20with%20the%20recent%20trends%20that%20show%20incidence%20of%20dementia%20decreasing%20in%20every%20decade.%20The%20risk%20of%20disease%20is%20also%20considerably%20low%20in%20younger%20generations%20because%20of%20their%20healthier%20lifestyles%20and%20upbringing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711606380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F9lq1qdao_brain-scan-generic-unsplash_625x300_30_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhuman-brains-getting-bigger-and-its-good-news-for-some-study-5325648%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20study%20also%20found%20that%20Generation%20X%20has%208%20per%20cent%20greater%20volume%20of%20white%20matter%20and%2015%20per%20cent%20more%20gray%20matter%20than%20the%20member%20of%20the%20previous%20generation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhuman-brains-getting-bigger-and-its-good-news-for-some-study-5325648%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20term%20as%20Pilibhit%20MP%20may%20be%20ending%2C%20but...'%3A%20BJP%20leader%20Varun%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711606273000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108840294%2Cimgsize-462077.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fup-lok-sabha-polls-my-term-as-pilibhit-mp-may-be-ending-but-will-continue-to-serve-says-bjp-leader-varun-gandhi-in-heartfelt-note%2Farticleshow%2F108840207.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fup-lok-sabha-polls-my-term-as-pilibhit-mp-may-be-ending-but-will-continue-to-serve-says-bjp-leader-varun-gandhi-in-heartfelt-note%2Farticleshow%2F108840207.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%2