n-internal-matters-5295329%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBlatant%20Interference%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20Protests%20Germany's%20Remarks%20On%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20last%20week%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20the%20third%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20after%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESebastian%20Fischer%2C%20a%20German%20foreign%20office%20spokesperson%2C%20on%20Saturday%20said%20it%20had%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20arrest%20and%20expects%20basic%20democratic%20principles%20to%20be%20applied%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20anyone%20facing%20accusations%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20entitled%20to%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20trial%2C%20this%20includes%20he%20can%20make%20use%20of%20all%20available%20legal%20avenues%20without%20restrictions.%20The%20presumption%20of%20innocence%20is%20a%20central%20element%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20must%20apply%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-enforcement-directorate-wants-to-arrest-arvind-kejriwal-5284508%5C%22%3EExplained%3A%20Why%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20Arrested%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prompted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-says-germanys-comment-on-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-blatant-interference-in-internal-matters-5295329%5C%22%3Equick%20backlash%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20India%20dubbing%20the%20remarks%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20interference%20in%20India's%20internal%20matters%26quot%3B.%20They%20also%20summoned%20the%20Deputy%20Head%20of%20Mission%20of%20the%20German%20Embassy%2C%20George%20Enzweiler%2C%20to%20lodge%20an%20official%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3