their%20waste%20to%20implementing%20measures%20to%20recharge%20groundwater%2C%20the%20mud%20homestay%20is%20raising%20the%20bar%20for%20nature-friendly%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspiration%20from%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20home%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kanyakumari%2C%20Rajchandar%20is%20a%20geo-data%20scientist%20who%20has%20spent%20the%20majority%20of%20his%20life%20around%20environmentalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSpending%20so%20much%20time%20around%20them%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20my%20home%20as%20aligned%20with%20nature%20as%20possible.%20I%20had%20always%20been%20concerned%20about%20the%20degradation%20of%20our%20environment%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20contribute%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajchandar%20fondly%20recalls%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273684%2Fbest-ecofriendly-homestay-munnar-book-treehouse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurrounded%20by%20greenery.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20has%20artefacts%20as%20old%20as%20100%20years.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345635%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20has%20artefacts%20as%20old%20as%20100%20years.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVisits%20to%20her%20home%20were%20my%20favourite%20part.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20unaware%20of%20how%20her%20deeply%20traditional%20and%20nature-friendly%20home%20would%20one%20day%20become%20an%20inspiration%20for%20my%20dream%20home%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20home%20was%20very%20simple%20with%20minimal%20use%20of%20cement%20and%20very%20traditional%20in%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20living%20in%20the%20city%2C%20he%20longed%20for%20a%20more%20secluded%20place%20surrounded%20by%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20village%20and%20the%20piece%20of%20land%20which%20now%20holds%20my%20home%2C%20it%20was%20like%20love%20at%20first%20sight.%20I%20could%20envision%20the%20future%20of%20the%20place%20and%20hence%20chose%20to%20buy%20the%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajchandar%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20very%20interesting%20story%20that%20goes%20around%20about%20the%20hills%20surrounding%20the%20area.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20when%20Lord%20Hanuman%20lifted%20the%20Dronagiri%20Parvat%20to%20take%20it%20to%20Lord%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20it%20broke%20off%20and%20fell%20here.%20Hence%2C%20these%20hills%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20medicinal%20plants%20growing%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20did%20not%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20area%20and%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20home%20that%20blends%20into%20nature%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20they%20started%20to%20work%20on%20their%20dream%20home%20and%20opened%20their%20doors%20to%20the%20g